description: This file defines a Jira frontend connector with methods for searching issues, creating issues, starting OAuth authentication, and disconnecting. It integrates with API utility functions and adheres to the FrontendConnector type.

methods.name: search
methods.description: Performs a search query for Jira issues via an API call, returning a list of normalized items.

methods.name: create
methods.description: Creates a new Jira issue with the provided project key, summary, and optional description.

methods.name: startOAuth
methods.description: Initiates OAuth login flow for Jira integration by retrieving the authorization URL.

methods.name: disconnect
methods.description: Disconnects the Jira connector by deleting its API connection.
